{"tid":12185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宅男玉蓮臺上吊亡 母親哭訴︰畀手機、網絡搞死","createTime":"2016-11-29T14:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T21:12:24.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"746b3c9e405c0a5b25e87b4c8daa503f93548c62","tid":12185,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:20:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>宅男玉蓮臺上吊亡 母親哭訴︰畀手機、網絡搞死</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-11-29 22:10:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n【22:08 更新】死者母親稱「依家啲人全部畀手機、網絡搞死咗。」她呼籲其他家長要主動與子女多溝通。【21:52】新增動新聞<br />\n<br />\n牛頭角一名隱閉青年昨晚被母親發現在寓所上吊身亡（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2fGlr4Y），警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，初步相信案件無可疑。母親事後忍喪子之痛表示：「以前冇隱閉青年㗎，唔會匿喺屋企，依家啲人全部畀手機、網絡搞死咗。」，她呼籲其他家長要主動與子女多溝通。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2fGlr4Y%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%A8%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%92%BF%E7%8D%B2%E9%81%BA%E6%9B%B8%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%9D%E6%AD%A5%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E6%A1%88%E4%BB%B6%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91%E3%80%82%E6%AF%8D%E8%A6%AA%E4%BA%8B%E5%BE%8C%E5%BF%8D%E5%96%AA%E5%AD%90%E4%B9%8B%E7%97%9B%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%86%87%E9%9A%B1%E9%96%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E3%97%8E%EF%BC%8C%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E5%8C%BF%E5%96%BA%E5%B1%8B%E4%BC%81%EF%BC%8C%E4%BE%9D%E5%AE%B6%E5%95%B2%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%95%80%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%81%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E6%90%9E%E6%AD%BB%E5%92%97%E3%80%82%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E5%A5%B9%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%88%87%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%9A%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E3%80%82&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=01e0fc85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2fGlr4Y），警方在現場未有撿獲遺書，初步相信案件無可疑。母親事後忍喪子之痛表示：「以前冇隱閉青年㗎，唔會匿喺屋企，依家啲人全部畀手機、網絡搞死咗。」，她呼籲其他家長要主動與子女多溝通。</a><br />\n<br />\n自縊身亡青年姓李（25歲），與父母及胞妹，住牛頭角花園大廈玉蓮臺2座一單位。據悉，李中五畢業後，一直沒有工作，常年足不出戶，是隱閉青年，其父親於年初病逝，母親從事夜更工作。現場所見其家門外貼有一張一家四口的圖畫，但一年內父子均離逝，街坊不勝欷歔。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚10時許，52歲姓吳母親回家時，驚見兒子在屋內用繩上吊自殺，連忙報案，惟救護員到場證實表年已身，吳婦傷心欲絕，她昨午接受訪問時稱：「以前冇隱閉青年㗎，唔會匿喺屋企，全部畀手機、網絡搞死咗。」她更強忍喪子之痛表示會堅強面對：「凡事應該由正面出發，積極去處理事情，唔好抱怨，唔好問點解，好多嘢無得點解」，又呼籲其他家長，要主動與子女多溝通。"},{"pid":"706e3dca82b7b0870016828e57dde7aeec601ec0","tid":12185,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"以前夠唔會老豆老母都要返工仲要淨係生一件"},{"pid":"1ad6e4f4e411ecba09f8873b3644a8e102b824bc","tid":12185,"uid":5932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"唔好問點解？我覺得個呀媽某程度上都有責任<br />\n一個正常家庭 有管教 個仔會做到宅男咁耐？"},{"pid":"b2d2f4ebcd7123669466404e269708c9543fd384","tid":12185,"uid":35285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:30:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66d27c6bd2d3a4539801aa96d3a7c7c1b642cb16","tid":12185,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32x579Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32x579Q.jpg&h=0f668117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c078e3ac3dbea421d6c963230abee9a1bbfb2e","tid":12185,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw想問下樓主唔使再比痴線bot屈毛感覺如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57c9c2760055477ceaa93f4f4d059d3574a43b6","tid":12185,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw想問下樓主唔使再比痴線bot屈毛感覺如何？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個件 holung乜 真係bot 狗黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見lihkg 唔少人post新聞 但回應既人好少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p